## Tables

You can use [tinytable](https://vincentarelbundock.github.io/tinytable/) for general tables and [modelsummary](https://vincentarelbundock.github.io/modelsummary/) for regression tables.
As @tbl-sum-penguins shows, the caption is displayed above the table.
The notes of the table can be added using the `notes` argument of the `tinytable::tt()` function.



::: {#tbl-sum-penguins .cell tbl-cap='Summary Statistics of Penguins'}
::: {.cell-output-display}

